  <li>Schedule a session with Dr. Meaghan Rice or another member of our team through the scheduling link on our site.</li>
  <li>Reach out via our contact form to ask questions or find out if we are a good fit for what you are facing.</li>
</ul>

<p>Winter is hard, but you do not have to go through it alone. We are here to help.</p>
